      • holdAndAdd

        BaseContainer<T> holdAndAdd(T element)
        Deprecated. 
        Holds element to be replaced and replace with the element. This method will replace last element in the list if it is full, other methods like add(Object) will return false if list is full.
        Parameters:
        element - Element to add.
        Returns:
        Container with replaced value (or empty container if there is not value to replace).
